channel.title: What do I need to open this? + Fog!
channel.description:
[IMG]http://i46.photobucket.com/albums/f144/rottenchild4/shops.jpg[/img] What do I do to open .CFG and CLASS files?
I use the Phonescape source, and i've never coded in my life, but Phonescape is the best and i've had it up for a couple days and people seem to like it.
Also, earlier, the server started acting weird. Now there is always fog. It never leaves, even if I restart. A lot of people are pressuring me to fix it, but I don't know how...

Okay For Your First Question, Just Click “Select A Program From List”, And Choose “NotePad”.

And For The Fog, Try Typing “::nofog” On Your Server, If That Doesn’t Work. On Your Server There Might Be A Folder Called “Weather”, Click It. And Try To Find Fog, Delete It.
